text: Maccabi Ahi Nazareth Football Club, Hebrew: מכבי אחי נצרת - Mo'adon Kaduregel Maccabi Aḥi Natzrat, Arabic: نادي كرة القدم اخاء الناصرة - Nade Korat Alqadam Maccabi Ekhaa Al-Nasera) is an Israeli football club in Nazareth. The club was established in 1968 and plays in the Liga Leumit. == Other websites == * Category:1968 establishments in Israel Category:Israeli football clubs Category:Nazareth
